# hello-flask

This is just super simple flask app.

## Requirements
- Python 3.6.3
- pipenv 8.2.6

## Development Setup
- You must set `FLASK_APP` environment variable first. Its value is `index.py`
- To create virtual environment for the first time, run `pipenv --three`
- Then install project dependencies, run `pipenv install`
- Activate the virtual environment, run `pipenv shell`
- Run the app `flask run`
- Head over to `http://localhost:5000`
